{"tid":2070220,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度媒體報導中國釋放10名印度戰俘 包括1中校3少校","createTime":"2020-06-19T03:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T11:00:48.000Z","uid":28765,"like":64,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"9ce71fc2ceae3b8aca57ad99c3c98cb02c9d3232","tid":2070220,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:39:07.000Z","msg":"即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國和印度近日在拉達克（Ladakh）加勒萬河谷（Galwan Valley）爆發衝突，印方至少有20人於這起高原肉搏戰喪命，兩國緊張關係逐漸加劇。印度媒體報導，中國18日釋放10名印度戰俘，包含1名中校和3名少校，意味著中方占據上風，印軍雖未證實，但表示印方沒有任何人失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n《印度人報》（The Hindu）報導，17日晚間中印軍隊進行少將級會談，兩國達成協議，18日下午5時左右，10名印度官兵被釋放，包含1名中校和3名少校，他們沒有受到任何傷害。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3202601\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3202601&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C0oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=6ef1324e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3202601&h=3ed3e365\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3202601</a>"},{"pid":"cf22d2b61365027af2db0c46d05e84d3d2f51fe1","tid":2070220,"uid":215876,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:40:02.000Z","msg":"戰狼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09376ddc161e95915e8bde3e0f29f06df9220f38","tid":2070220,"uid":73340,"like":113,"dislike":3,"score":110,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:41:18.000Z","msg":"其實係唔係已經打緊仗<br />\n但D消息唔浮出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無啦啦又會有10個俘虜"},{"pid":"eeb1a71e65dc4d520b4a1311c6f9bb61b98ef42f","tid":2070220,"uid":37666,"like":33,"dislike":4,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"09376ddc161e95915e8bde3e0f29f06df9220f3